php_exec: several methods to run external program in php
========================================================

Several methods to run external program in PHP

Snippets
========

$stdout = shell_exec($cmd);

$last = exec($cmd, $stdout_lines, $status);

ob_start();
$last = system($cmd, $status);
$stdout = ob_get_clean();

ob_start();
passthru($cmd, $status)
$stdout = ob_get_clean();

